  "title": "Core Concepts",
  "lessonText": "In this lesson, we will explore the fundamental concepts of Python essential for game development.",
  "data": {
    "content": "## Core Concepts of Python\n- **Variables**: Store data values.\n- **Data Types**: Common types include integers, floats, strings, and booleans.\n- **Operators**: Perform operations on variables and values.\n- **Control Flow**: Use `if`, `else`, and `elif` statements for decision-making.\n- **Loops**: Implement `for` and `while` loops for repetitive tasks.\n- **Functions**: Define reusable blocks of code using `def` keyword.\n- **Modules**: Organize code into separate files for better structure."
  }
